LABOTS
======

IRC bot framework written in python 3.x, just works for myself.


Features
--------

* Run multiple bots with single IRC bot
* Useful IRC bot interface
* Dynamic {load,unload} bots (Pyinotify)
* Asynchronous socket and IO (Tornado)


Requires
--------

* Python 3
* Pyinotify >= 0.9.4
* Tornado >= 3.2.2


Usage
-----

Run LABots: change field in `config.py`, and run `./labots.py`.

    e.g:
        host = 'irc.freenode.net'
        port = 6666
        nick = 'labots'
        path = 'bots'

    LABots will loads all bot scripts in `bots` directory, when script file
    (*.py) or configure file (*.json) changed, bot script will be reload
    automatically. file which name starts with `_` or `.` will be ignored.

Write a bot: Please see `bots/example.py`
    or <https://github.com/lastavenger/bots>


Bots
----

See <https://github.com/LastAvenger/bots>.


